1. Vreme se *približava* proleću. (Time is *approaching* spring.)
2. On se *približava* meni. (He is *approaching* me.)
3. Kompanija se *približava* cilju. (The company is *approaching* its goal.)
4. *Približavao* sam se, ali sam se ipak okrenuo. (I *approached* but then turned around.)
5. Ona se *približavala* sa osmehom na licu. (She *approached* with a smile on her face.)
6. Voz se *približavao* stanici. (The train *approached* the station.)
7. Košarkaši se *približavaju* kraju sezone. (The basketball players are *approaching* the end of the season.)
8. Mračni oblaci se *približavaju* gradu. (Dark clouds are *approaching* the city.)
9. *Približavajući* se kraju, shvatio sam da sam pogrešio. (*Approaching* the end, I realized I was wrong.)
10. Uspeli smo da se *približimo* svom cilju. (We managed to *approach* our goal.)